Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,德文\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Devon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不...听着 我们不开心 我们很痛苦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, no, no. Listen, we're not happy. We're miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伯特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Burt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在地下折磨我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}They torture us down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,德文\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Devon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们都是囚犯 - 伯特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- We're prisoners! - Burt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(健康部)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(宏观数据精检部)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你就是马克S\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I suppose you're Mark S.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我... - 我是马克W\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- I-- - I'm Mark W.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是谁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意换个名字\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Would you be open to using a different first name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,以避免混淆吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}to avoid confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 马克S\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Welcome back, Mark S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Been a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们去哪了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得 还是等到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think it's best to save any queries
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去了管理层办公室再问问题吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}till we arrive at the management office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他们被辞退了吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Were they fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以把气球放在我旧桌子边的门厅里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can leave the balloons in the foyer by my old desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有许多要讨论的事 别让气球分了你的心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've much to discuss, and I don't want them distracting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证 不会拿走你的气球的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I assure you, they won't be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,米尔奇克先生 拜托了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Milchick, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们五个月前做的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What you all did five months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是这家公司历史上最痛苦的时刻之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}was one of the most painful moments in the history of this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,五个月\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Five months?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也因此受到了影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I, too, was wounded by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但不经历痛苦就无法治愈 对吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we must be cut to heal, mustn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你刚说你的“旧办公室”\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wait, did you say your old office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,马克 这是黄小姐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mark, this is Miss Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,黄小姐 这是马克S\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Miss Huang, Mark S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊的时候 可以请她保管你的气球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}She'll be happy to mind your balloons while we chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这边 马克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Right this way, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以关上门\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can shut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这正常吗 让小孩...\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is it normal for a child to--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,房间很乱 你别介意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Excuse the clutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 到底是怎么回事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay. What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,科贝尔女士已经从公司离职了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ms. Cobel is no longer with this company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我是分离楼层的主管\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I now manage the severed floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的团队呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What about my team?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有辞退他们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We didn't fire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,赫莉R和欧文B都成功与外面的人联络上了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Helly R. and Irving B. both successfully made contact with persons on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}just as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,迪伦G外面的自己在事后得知发生了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dylan G.'s outie learned what happened after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都知道你们四人了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}The four of you have achieved international fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们作为一个团体出名了 成了分离改革的带路人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}As a group, you've become known as the face of severance reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,(“里面的自己”成为吹哨人)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 分离改... - 马克 坐吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Severance ref-- - Have a seat, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们叛变之后 我们安装了安全门\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Shortly before your mutiny, we installed security doors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,保证你们不离开宏观数据精检\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}to keep you in MDR.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,此外 科贝尔女士 还会唱诵基尔圣歌的惩罚版本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}This accompanied a punitive rendition of the Kier hymn performed by Ms. Cobel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你记得吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你锁在房间里 像牲畜一样 马克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I locked you in a room like an animal, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个未分离的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}As an unsevered man,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都会记得这件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll carry that knowledge the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但过去五个月\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But for the past five months,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在自问 像哈蒙妮科贝尔这样的虐待狂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}we've been asking how a sadist like Harmony Cobel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎能在卢蒙的土壤上扎根和生长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}could take fertile root in Lumon soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明我们是哪种公司\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what that says about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也知道 你在你妹妹家醒来时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We also know Ms. Cobel was at your sister's home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,科贝尔女士也在场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}when you awoke there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对 为什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah. Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为她对你产生了一种痴迷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We believe she'd developed an erotic fixation on you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,计划追求你和你外面的自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}and had plans to pursue both you and your outie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你们成为“三人情侣”\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}in what might be termed "a throuple."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好她没有成功\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thankfully, she failed at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没说我的团队去哪儿了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You still haven't told me where my team is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们努力了几周 想要召回他们 马克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We tried for weeks to get them back, Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都不同意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}None of them agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和他们说会进行改革 但那还是不够\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We told them of the reforms, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Except for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你外面的自己坚持要回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your outie insisted on returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 他求我们立即让他回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, he begged us to let him back right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,所以其他人...都拒绝了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the others, they refused?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听他们亲口说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, I'd like to hear it from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受你的气球吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Enjoy your balloons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们在你来大约一小时前到的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah. We showed up about an hour before you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和原来的宏观数据精检比起来 这里有点狭小\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a little cramped compared to our old MDR,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但我喜欢绿色的地毯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I love the green carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的地毯是焦糖奶油色 键盘是紫红色的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ours was a crème br?lée and the keyboards were puce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是紫色\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}They were purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是紫红色 我知道 因为那颜色令我眩晕\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. They were puce. I know because it makes me nauseous,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也讨厌甜点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I hate sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说到甜点 我们多长时间 会见到一次那个“米奇”先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Speaking of which, how much do we see of that Mr. "Milkshake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,米尔奇克先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Milchick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是米尔奇克 不是米奇 我不知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's Milchick, not milkshake. And I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,马尔克 哪里能找到墨水 还有铅笔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Marco, where I can find some ink pencils?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,文具柜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supply closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll show ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以你真见到外面的世界了  - 是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- So, did you really see the outie world? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,天空是什么样的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}How's the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,(储存柜)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么 你没见到  - 我是去了外面一小会儿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- What, you didn't see it? - Well, I went outside for a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但被我的妹夫转移了注意力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I was distracted by my brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们列了一份清单 写着我们最想在外面看到什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Because we made a list of what we'd most like to see on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,天空显然是第一位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And sky was an easy number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没有“妹夫”这一项\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Brothers-in-law weren't even on the list.
