Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.57,0:27:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最优等的分离工作环境之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the 206 countries from which Lumon operates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.74,0:27:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 不准在走廊跑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, no running in my halls!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.87,0:27:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好痒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.25,0:27:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但什么才能让一栋建筑真的快乐呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what makes a building truly happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.17,0:27:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,四位宏观数据精检员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}This question came to light when four MDR workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.51,0:27:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对分离的生活感到不满意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}dissatisfied with their severed lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.55,0:27:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,于是一起想出一个阴谋 卢蒙历史学家将称其为“宏观数起义”\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}conspired to mount what Lumon historians will forever call
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.77,0:27:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题因此也有了答案\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Macrodat Uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.23,0:27:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我的鼻子下 上演了一出 充满危险和阴谋的人类戏剧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Under my literal nose unfolded a human drama of danger and intrigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.40,0:27:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,正义的愤怒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Righteous anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.28,0:27:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们把这里夷为平地吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let's burn this place to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,灵感\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.87,0:27:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么在对真相一无所知中工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why are we down here still working in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.09,0:27:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,和爱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么鬼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What the shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.72,0:28:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宏观数起义掀起了改革的新风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Macrodat Uprising yielded bounteous reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.44,0:28:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,包括新的美味小食 比如果皮干 青豆罐头\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}These include tasty new snacks, like fruit leather, cut beans,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.61,0:28:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞薄荷和莎莎酱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Christmas mints, and salsa.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.41,0:28:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什...\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wh--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.20,0:28:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还没说服你吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not sold yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.29,0:28:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,(卢蒙走廊通行证)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.37,0:28:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,员工奖励也进行了改革\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}The incentives were also reformed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在加入了走廊通行证 咬菠萝游戏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}and now range from hall passes to pineapple bobbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.72,0:28:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还有全新的哈哈镜屋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}to our brand-new playful mirror room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.89,0:28:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其实说来有趣 我一辈子 都坐在这个倒影池旁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, it's funny. I've sat by this reflective pool my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.02,0:28:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但直到四位宏观数据精检英雄 展现无声的勇气后 我才真正看清自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}yet it took the quiet courage of four MDR heroes to show me who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.74,0:29:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们“一石激起千层浪”\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}They made quite a splash.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.32,0:29:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,说的真对 水塔 为他们 我要感谢基尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}They sure did, Water Tower. And I thank Kier for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为宏观数起义 我要感谢基尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I thank Kier for the Macrodat Uprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们之间有意见分歧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know we have our differences...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但希望你们明白 我真正尊重你们每一个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I want you to know that I truly respect each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.28,0:29:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想成为你们的狱卒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I don't wanna be your jailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.49,0:29:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,今天结束时 你们每个人 将选择是否继续留在公司\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}By end of day, each of you will choose whether you want to remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.16,0:29:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你们外面的自己 而是你们自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Not your outies, but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.17,0:29:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们开始处理文件 那我就会当你们选择留下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you start work on your file, I'll assume you want to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.00,0:30:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,否则 我会让你们去地上 没有任何恶意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}If not, I'll send you to the surface. No ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.80,0:30:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定有一天 我会在餐厅请你们喝一杯呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe I'll even buy you a drink at a bistro one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.14,0:30:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就像分离楼层的其他部分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like the rest of the severed floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.97,0:30:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,休息室没有摄像头 也没有麦克风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}the break room has no cameras or microphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该留更多空间给个人隐私\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Privacy shouldn't mean packing into a supply closet
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.06,0:30:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是把它挤得像罐头沙丁鱼一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}like so many sardines.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.95,0:30:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我真心希望你们都选择留下 一起享受你们帮助建造的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I truly hope you all will choose to stay and enjoy what you've helped build.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.12,0:30:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,新的季度 新的开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}A new quarter. A fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.67,0:30:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起努力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才都是什么鬼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是和我们玩重量级心理战呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Massive-ass head game is what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.98,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们在上面都看到了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So what the hell did you guys see up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.69,0:31:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这...\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.77,0:31:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他说这里没有麦克风\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}He said there were no microphones in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.28,0:31:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是 他说的大话多了去了 所以你就压低声音说吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, he says a lot of shit, so just fucking whisper it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.74,0:31:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.90,0:31:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在我妹妹家里 参加为里肯黑尔举行的派对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, I was at a party at my sister's house for Ricken Hale.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.20,0:31:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.79,0:31:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识里肯黑尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know Ricken Hale?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.12,0:31:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我外面自己的妹夫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}He's my outie's brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.21,0:31:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何 我们都认识科贝尔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And for some reason, we both know Cobel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.84,0:31:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,太疯狂了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对 还有一件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah. Well, there's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.01,0:31:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我换回来之前 我发现了一张婚礼照片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just before I switched back, I found a wedding photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.97,0:31:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我外面的自己的妻子几年前去世了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, I guess my outie's wife died a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.73,0:31:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.31,0:31:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而那似乎就是我决定接受分离的部分原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which, apparently, is part of why I decided to get severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.02,0:31:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.19,0:31:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,照片中的女人是凯西女士\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}the woman in the photo was Ms. Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.08,0:31:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,凯西女士是你的妻子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ms. Casey is your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:31:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是我外面的自己的妻子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is my outie's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.91,0:32:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但她死了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.50,0:32:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知道 但就是她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, I know, but it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.01,0:32:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可她在地下啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then she's down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.88,0:32:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我去了健康部 那里没了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. I went to Wellness. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.76,0:32:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么叫没了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you mean, gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.97,0:32:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没有那个地方了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.48,0:32:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 马克 你还好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, my God. Mark, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.61,0:32:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我不知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah. Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.32,0:32:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 你看到了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What about you? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.32,0:32:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I saw the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一个很无聊的公寓内部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}of a really fucking boring apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.42,0:32:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你独自一人住\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, you live by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.54,0:32:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.67,0:32:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在看某个电视节目 关于大自然的 我穿着运动裤和T恤衫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was watching some nature show on TV, wearing sweatpants and a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.30,0:32:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种T恤衫  上面有乐队或口袋什么的吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What kind of T-shirt? Did it feature, like, a band or pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.51,0:32:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,类似“救救大猩猩”的那种T恤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was like a "save the gorillas" shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.77,0:33:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,酷啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.19,0:33:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.69,0:33:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我出门 看到了一个人 他看起来像个园丁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then I went outside and found a guy. He looked like a gardener.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.49,0:33:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一切都告诉了他 我觉得他好像不相信\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Told him everything. I think he kind of thought it was bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.74,0:33:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 他说他哥哥是警察\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But he said that his brother was a cop
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.99,0:33:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他会把一切都告诉他哥哥\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that he would tell him everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.16,0:33:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 抱歉 我真的努力了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't know. Sorry, guys. I really tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.50,0:33:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,园丁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}A gardener?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.26,0:33:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.18,0:33:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上工作的园丁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}A night gardener?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.22,0:33:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是的 也许他白天有别的工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think so. I mean, maybe he has a different job during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 欧文\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What about you, Irv?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.82,0:33:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们觉得他是认真的吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you suppose he's serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.24,0:33:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说我们可以离开那话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}About letting us leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.79,0:34:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,欧文 你看到了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Irv, what did you see?
