Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.48,0:42:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我理解... - 米尔奇克先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Well, I sympathize... - Mr. Milchick--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.98,0:42:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但你能确保处理好这个问题吗 是 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}...but could you please see that it's taken care of? Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.16,0:42:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人打来说开机画面的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}If someone calls about my welcome screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.57,0:42:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,立即给我转接\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I need you to put that call through immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.28,0:42:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是 先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.29,0:42:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想见我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.29,0:42:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.38,0:42:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 黄小姐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you, Miss Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.51,0:42:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你要为皮带的事道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You gonna apologize about the belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.61,0:42:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子叫格雷琴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your wife's name is Gretchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.61,0:42:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.82,0:42:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她希望你知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}She wanted you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.83,0:43:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.34,0:43:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 我的确要道歉 迪伦 因为我没有用心聆听\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I do apologize, Dylan, for not being a better listener.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.47,0:43:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没有听到你的需求\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}For not hearing your needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.14,0:43:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,(外面的家庭探访套间)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.73,0:43:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是新装修工程的设计图\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}These are blueprints for a new renovation,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.03,0:43:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我选择不告知你的同事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}of which I chose not to inform your colleagues.
