Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.95,0:43:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,它叫外面的家庭探访套间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's called the Outie Family Visitation Suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.57,0:43:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(回忆墙)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.58,0:43:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说 可以在地下看到我的家人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you saying I could see my family here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.04,0:43:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,按房间的字面意思 是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}If you take the name of the room at face value, I'd say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.38,0:43:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老天爷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Holy fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.30,0:43:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}The holiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.72,0:44:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很可惜 你们部门的其他人都是单身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sadly, everyone else in your department is single.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.39,0:44:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 我要请你不将此事告诉别人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}As such, I'm asking that you keep this between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.35,0:44:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是... - 只是为了避免嫉恨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are you-- - ...only to avoid resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.52,0:44:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你为朋友们做了那么多 我可不希望他们与你反目\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'd hate for your friends to turn against you after all you've done for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.41,0:45:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.58,0:45:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm okay.
